It's great to hear from you! I'm doing well, thanks for asking. 

It looks like you were quite active in September, especially on the 13th with 15600 steps! You also had some impressive step counts on the 8th, 9th, and 14th. It's great to see you getting those steps in. 

Now, to answer your question, I do not have access to your step count for November 17, 2024. If you have any other questions related to health and fitness, feel free to ask!
